2 Né 3:6–15</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.8-11?lang=fra#p8\">3 Né 21:8–11</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.16,25?lang=fra#p16\">Mrm 8:16, 25</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"9\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note9a\" data-full-marker=\"9a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117792420\" id=\"note9a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/salvation-for-the-dead?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Salut pour les morts</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note9b\" data-full-marker=\"9b\">\n<p data-aid=\"117792424\" id=\"note9b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5?lang=fra#p5\">2 Né 3:5</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note9c\" data-full-marker=\"9c\">\n<p data-aid=\"117792427\" id=\"note9c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ezek/34.14?lang=fra#p14\">Éz 34:14</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"11\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note11a\" data-full-marker=\"11a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117792430\" id=\"note11a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/62.10?lang=fra#p10\">És 62:10</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.23-32?lang=fra#p23\">D&amp;A 133:23–32</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"12\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note12a\" data-full-marker=\"12a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117792433\" id=\"note12a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/43.5-6?lang=fra#p5\">És 43:5–6</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"13\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note13a\" data-full-marker=\"13a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117792437\" id=\"note13a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/44.23?lang=fra#p23\">És 44:23</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</u